ption\":\"Among Concord's top-rated facilities, Camp Happy Hound excels in year-round care. This facility features air-conditioned spaces for hot summers, North Carolina pet care professionals, offering pet...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Concord\",\"addressRegion\":\"NC\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/camp-happy-hound/camp-happy-hound-1.jpg\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where is the dog park in Concord, NC?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Weddington Road Bark Park is the primary off-leash facility, featuring separate areas for large and small dogs. Frank Liske Park also has a smaller dog run.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I walk my dog at Frank Liske Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, Frank Liske Park is a massive recreational area perfect for leashed walks around the lake and playing fields. It’s a local favorite for active dog owners.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed at Charlotte Motor Speedway?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Generally, pets are allowed in the camping areas during race weeks but are restricted from the grandstands. Always check specific event rules before bringing your pet.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is there a greenway in Concord?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, the Hector H. Henry II Greenway offers paved trails that connect neighborhoods and parks, providing a safe, car-free environment for dog walking.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Park