swer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Weddington Road Bark Park is the primary off-leash facility, featuring separate areas for large and small dogs. Frank Liske Park also has a smaller dog run.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Can I walk my dog at Frank Liske Park?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes, Frank Liske Park is a massive recreational area perfect for leashed walks around the lake and playing fields. It’s a local favorite for active dog owners.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Are dogs allowed at Charlotte Motor Speedway?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Generally, pets are allowed in the camping areas during race weeks but are restricted from the grandstands. Always check specific event rules before bringing your pet.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Is there a greenway in Concord?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes, the Hector H. Henry II Greenway offers paved trails that connect neighborhoods and parks, providing a safe, car-free environment for dog walking.\\\"}}]}26:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$2e\\\"}}]\\n27:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"itemListElement\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":1,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Home\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\\\\\"},{\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"ListItem\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"position\\\\\\\":2,\\\\\\\"name\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"item\\\\\